  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat. Add onion and garlic, sauté until softened.",
    "Stir in cream cheese and smoked paprika. Cook for an additional 2 minutes or until the mixture is smooth and slightly heated.",
    "Fold in spinach leaves and cook until wilted. Stir in fresh parsley and oregano just before serving to prevent browning.",
    "Serve hot with crusty bread."
